blocks.en:
flowchart TD
    S[Start: MPX IE received] --> TT{Transfer Type?}
    TT -->|0b110| AB[Return abort for Transaction ID]
    TT -->|0b000/0b001| DLV[Deliver single-frame payload]
    TT -->|0b010/0b100| FF{First fragment?}
    FF -->|Yes 0b010 frag0| SEC{Security params ok?}
    SEC -->|match| ASM[Start assembly buffer]
    SEC -->|differ| DR[Drop: inconsistent security]
    FF -->|No| CFN{Fragment number ok?}
    CFN -->|new| APP[Append to MPX list]
    CFN -->|retransmit / skipped| DR2[Drop frame]

blocks.zh:
flowchart TD
    S[开始: 收到 MPX IE] --> TT{Transfer Type?}
    TT -->|0b110| AB[返回该事务中止]
    TT -->|0b000/0b001| DLV[交付单帧负载]
    TT -->|0b010/0b100| FF{是否首分片?}
    FF -->|是 0b010 分片0| SEC{安全参数一致?}
    SEC -->|一致| ASM[启动重组缓冲区]
    SEC -->|不一致| DR[丢弃: 安全参数不符]
    FF -->|否| CFN{分片号是否正确?}
    CFN -->|新分片| APP[追加到 MPX 列表]
    CFN -->|重传/跳号| DR2[丢弃帧]
